File			Content

hermes-config.xml 	Basic configuration with just a file provider.
web-hermes-config.xml 	Configuration used for the screenshots on the website.
ems-hermes-config.xml 	Example Tibco EMS configuration. See also http://www.hermesjms.com/demos/ems_1_9.html
jboss-hermes-config.xml Example JBossMQ with their own JNDI provider and the Sun reference filesystem provider.

log4j.ant.props 	Log4j settings when usign Hermes Ant tasks

sonicmq.jndi.properties Example provider property file for use when configuring SonicMQ with JNDI.